    Read only data object for data of BLE discovery and resolving process.

    OutputElement is returned by callbacks of the BlukiiClient functions for discovery and resolve of BLE modules.

    It is an combination of data that is encapsulated in specific data objects:
    • InputElement: input data that is created by discovery process (blukii number) or external inputs (NFC tag id, scan of barcodes).
      A conversion of the InputElement.getTagID() is returned by getId().

    • DiscoveryData: emitted data of the BLE module

    • ResolveData: resolved data requested from blukii Info Manager (https://manager.blukiiinfo.com)
      The state of resolve process is returned by getResolveState().
